description: Lubricant tycoon Drake Barrrington (Billy Santoro) has it all: a life of luxury, decadence, and debauchery. It’s a life he’s ready to share with his soon-to-be husband, Kristoffer Jennings (Drae Axtell) -- but just when life seems to be a wet dream come true… ENTER ALEX! Alex Barrington (James Castle), Drake’s hot-tempered first husband, returns to makes things as sticky and slippery as the lube magnate could imagine. These three are ready to dine on drama, and on ass.
title: Dine Ass-ty | Drae Axtell, James Castle, Billy Santoro
